export const randomCoordinates = () => {
    const famousPlaces = [
        { lat: 40.689247, lon: -74.044502 }, // Statue of Liberty, New York, USA
        { lat: 37.819929, lon: -122.478255 }, // Golden Gate Bridge, San Francisco, USA
        { lat: 43.642566, lon: -79.387057 }, // CN Tower, Toronto, Canada
        { lat: 36.106965, lon: -112.112997 }, // Grand Canyon, Arizona, USA
        { lat: 44.4280, lon: -110.5885 }, // Yellowstone National Park, USA
        { lat: 20.684285, lon: -88.567783 }, // Chichen Itza, Yucatan, Mexico
        { lat: 43.096214, lon: -79.037739 }, // Niagara Falls, Canada/USA
        { lat: 43.879102, lon: -103.459067 }, // Mount Rushmore, South Dakota, USA
        { lat: 28.385233, lon: -81.563874 }, // Disney World, Orlando, USA
        { lat: 51.496846, lon: -115.928056 }, // Banff National Park, Alberta, Canada
        { lat: 47.620506, lon: -122.349277 }, // Space Needle, Seattle, USA
        { lat: 37.826977, lon: -122.422956 }, // Alcatraz Island, San Francisco, USA
        { lat: 34.134115, lon: -118.321548 }, // Hollywood Sign, Los Angeles, USA
        { lat: 34.055345, lon: -118.249845 }, // Walt Disney Concert Hall, Los Angeles, USA
        { lat: 38.889939, lon: -77.009051 } // Capitol Hill, Washington, D.C., USA
      ];
      return famousPlaces
}
